- DITs and on-set technicians: ensure consistent monitoring and dailies.

WHAT PROBLEM IT SOLVES
Replaces Canon’s proprietary SDK-dependent log inverse with an open, verified
mathematical transform. Correctly models the DGO sensor’s unique behavior,
ensuring that C700 footage linearized via GIOP matches the original scene light
to within 10⁻⁶ relative error. Provides dual log curve support, enabling
workflows that mix Log 2 (VFX pulls) and Log 3 (grading) with a single
auditable IDT.

